datasets.name: dataset_9
queryLines: SELECT DATE_TRUNC('MONTH', `First Device Event Date Time`) AS `Month(First Device Event Date Time)`, `Months Since First Use` AS `Months Since First Use`, `Session Type` AS `Session Type`, `Weeks Since First Use` AS `Weeks Since First Use`, MEASURE(`Active_Devices`) AS `Active Devices`, (MEASURE(`Active_Devices`) / SUM(MEASURE(`Active_Devices`)) OVER (PARTITION BY `First Device Event Date Time`)) * 100 AS `% Devices Returning` FROM `workspace.default.HPX_Retention_CSS_Analytics` WHERE `First Device Event Date Time` >= '2023-05-01' GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC('MONTH', `First Device Event Date Time`), `Months Since First Use`, `Session Type`, `Weeks Since First Use` ORDER BY `Month(First Device Event Date Time)`

fields.name: % Devices Returning
fields.expression: (MEASURE(`Active_Devices`) / SUM(MEASURE(`Active_Devices`)) OVER (PARTITION BY `First Device Event Date Time`)) * 100
